snippet.title: Critter Cove - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Critter Cove is a life simulation exploration game developed by Gentleman Rat. Players are tasked with rebuilding an island town alongside a huge cast of charming residents. Explore a mysterious and vibrant island and set sail to discover relics, craft items, and meet new people on your journey. Critter Cove is launching in 2023 for PC with Steam Closed Beta Signups available now.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
